    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's still feeling a bit weird, my neck feels a little stiff too, maybe from sitting at the desk too long? but i really need to focus. if i take a double dose of ibuprofen now it'll probably knock this out and i can finish my chapters, right? i just want to make sure i'm making the right call so i don't feel like crap during the test tomorrow.",
