      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You should absolutely not take a double dose of ibuprofen; that is a dangerous over-medication. Stiffness in the neck combined with a severe headache warrants more than just painkillers. Try a gentle neck stretch while you sip on some warm water, and consider taking a short, 20-minute power nap to reset your system. If the neck stiffness and headache don't improve after that rest, you need to seriously reconsider pushing through the study session.",
